<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Unread Message Reminder</title>

    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f4f6f8;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 30px auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      }

      .header {
        background-color: #01868f;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #ffffff;
      }

      .header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 22px;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 25px;
        color: #333333;
      }

      .content p {
        font-size: 15px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }

      .highlight {
        background-color: #f1f5ff;
        padding: 15px;
        border-left: 4px solid #01868f;
        border-radius: 4px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }

      .button-wrapper {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 25px 0;
      }

      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        background-color: #01868f;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: bold;
        border-radius: 6px;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
      }

      .button:hover {
        background-color: #01868f;
      }

      .footer {
        background-color: #f9fafb;
        padding: 15px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #777777;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="header">
        <h1>📩 You Have an Unread Message</h1>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hi <strong><%= receiverName %></strong>,</p>

        <p>
          This is a quick reminder to let you know that you have an unread
          message waiting for you.
        </p>

        <div class="highlight">
			<p>💬 <strong>Message:</strong> <%= message %></p>
        </div>
		<p> <strong>Message from:</strong> <%= sender %></p>

        <p>Please check your inbox to view and respond to the message.</p>
        <p>
          If you’ve already seen this message, you can safely ignore this email.
        </p>

        <p>Thanks,<br /><strong>The PB Team</strong></p>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated reminder. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
